@tasca/execution
================

This package vendors and overlays a soft fork of:

    Emdash
    https://github.com/generalaction/emdash
    Copyright (c) Emdash Contributors / General Action, Inc.
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The upstream source is included verbatim as a pinned git submodule at:

    vendor/emdash   (tag v0.4.48, commit 67ab3a86f7469f4a91200dadf50293b4be3d90d9)

No modifications are made to the upstream source. The de-Electron capability
is delivered entirely as an additive overlay under src/ (an Electron stub,
a module-resolution bootstrap, a SecretStore, a typed ExecutionPort, and a
build script). See vendor/emdash/LICENSE.md for the full Apache-2.0 text and
src/runtime/ for the overlay.

